Package edu.brown.cs.mramesh4.maps

Class WayNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.mramesh4.maps.WayNodes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Dimensional, GraphNode<WayNodes,​Way>
    public class WayNodes
extends Object
implements Dimensional, GraphNode<WayNodes,​Way>
    This class represents a Node object from the database. It implements GraphNode so that it can be used in our generic Graph class.
